completed to date. The list includes the target company, the
principal acquirer, the dollar value and the year completed, or
whether the deal is pending.
   _RJR Nabisco Inc., by Kohlberg Kravis Roberts &amp; Co., $24.5
billion, completed in 1989.
   _BAT Industries PLC, by Hoylake Investments PLC, $21 billion,
pending.
