   _Gulf Corp., by Standard Oil Co. of California (now Chevron
Corp.), $13.4 billion, completed in 1984.
   _Kraft Inc., by Philip Morris Cos., $12.9 billion, completed in
1988
   _Time Inc., by Paramount Communications Inc., $12.2 billion,
pending.
   _Getty Oil Co., by Texaco Inc., $10.1 billion, completed in 1984.
   _Dome Petroleum Ltd., by Amoco Canada, $9.02 billion, completed
in 1988.
   _Standard Oil Co. (45 percent), by British Petroleum Corp.
(already held 55 percent), $7.9 billion, completed in 1987.
   _Smithkline Beckman Corp., merger with Beecham Group PLC, $7.82
billion, pending.
   _Conoco Inc., by DuPont Co., $7.4 billion, completed in 1981.
   _Federated Department Stores Corp., by Campeau Corp., $6.58
billion, completed in 1988.
   _Marathon Oil Co., by USX, $6.5 billion, completed in 1982.
   _RCA Corp., by General Electric Co., $6.4 billion, completed in
1986.
   _Beatrice Cos., by Kohlberg Kravis Roberts, $6.1 billion,
completed in 1986.
